          "currentValue": "Valta Property Valuations Ltd. is proud to present the appraisal report that satisfies the agreed upon scope of work with 1021098645 Saskatchewan Ltd. The purpose of this assignment is to provide the As Stabilized current market value of the subject property, which at the time of inspection represents the improved property as of the effective date and is leased up at market rental rates and operating costs for the property located at 1101, 1121 109 St, North Battleford, SK (herein after referred to as the subject property).",
