        {
          "selector": ".letter-body p:nth-of-type(3)",
          "fieldId": "property-description",
          "currentValue": "The subject property, located at 1101, 1121 109 St, North Battleford, SK, is a multi-family, walkup property with improvements located in North Battleford. The improvements are comprised of 2 total buildings, and consist of 19,204 square feet of rentable area (NRA) as of the valuation date. The property, reportedly built in 1970 (1970 weighted) is approximately 100.0% occupied and features 16 units in a 2-story, garden style format.",
